        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Rearrange per-dimension quantized query codes into bit-plane layout.</para>
<para><computeroutput>rotated_qq</computeroutput> holds one qb-bit code per dimension (one byte each, value in [0, 2^qb)). <computeroutput>out</computeroutput> receives qb bit-planes of ((d + 7) / 8) bytes each: bit-plane j packs bit j of code i into bit (i % 8) of byte (i / 8). <computeroutput>out</computeroutput> must have room for qb * ((d + 7) / 8) bytes and is fully overwritten.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>rotated_qq</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>per-dimension codes (d bytes) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>d</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>dimensionality </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>qb</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>quantization bits per dimension (1..8) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>out</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>bit-plane output buffer (qb * ((d + 7) / 8) bytes) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
